{{Quote|Great. We stumbled into their airborne infantry training school. Could've been worse, I suppose. Could've been an artillery range...|[[Darth Caedus|Jacen Solo]]|<ref name="The New Jedi Order: Traitor">''[[The New Jedi Order: Traitor]]''</ref>}}
'''Yuuzhan Vong paratroopers''' were [[Yuuzhan Vong]] soldiers trained to jump from special coralcraft onto a planet's surface, using silken canopies to slow their descent. While on [[Coruscant/Legends#Yuuzhan'tar|Yuuzhan'tar]], [[Darth Caedus|Jacen Solo]] and [[Vergere]] saw a mass paratrooper drop, which Jacen initially mistook for a training exercise. Actually, the paratroopers were searching for him.

==Appearances==
